{"title":"麦收农谚","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收农谚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收有五忙：割、拉、晒、碾、藏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉在场里一半，放在囤里才算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收有两怕：天晴、天下。（注一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八成割，十成收；十成割，八成收。（注二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）天晴风干，易使麦粒脱落。“天下”指阴雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）“八成割”中的“八成”是指小麦成熟度。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}